metadata.description: World-renowned, pop-street artist Jisbar made history by bringing his art to outer space, and now heâ€™s bringing it to the blockchain. From acrylic paint to Web3, from the Louvre to Cardi B, Mona Lisart by Jisbar is about the art. 10 years of mastery, encapsulated in one collection of 10,000 NFTs showcasing his most famous exhibitions & collaborations, accessible to the public, for the first time in history. Each unique hand-drawn piece of digital art from the collection corresponds to a claimable piece of physical art based on the rarity of the NFT. https://monalisart.io
